{
  "texts": [
    "Scalability remains a significant challenge.",
    "Approaches like Delay Compensated Adam (DC-Adam) have been proposed to address resource constraints on edge devices (Tian et al. 2021).",
    "Techniques such as reinforcement learning have improved the handling of non-IID data, particularly in client selection.",
    "Models like FedEx and AnoFed enhance explainability and adaptive detection.",
    "These features make Auto Encoder well-suited for real-time, highinterpretability applications in industrial control systems and healthcare."
  ]
}